     C           *IN20     IFEQ '0'
     C                     MOVELM1KENO    PPKENO
     C                     MOVEL'D'       M1SKJY
     C                     Z-ADD*YEAR     M1SKYY
     C                     Z-ADDUMONTH    M1SKMM
     C                     Z-ADDUDAY      M1SKDD
     C                     UPDATMRAPL011
     C                     ENDIF
      * BLANK PART NO.
     C                     MOVELPPKENO    #KKENO
     C                     MOVEL'1'       #KKENA
     C           KEYM12    CHAINMRAPL021             20
     C           *IN20     IFEQ '0'
     C                     MOVEL'D'       M1SKJY
     C                     Z-ADD*YEAR     M1SKYY
     C                     Z-ADDUMONTH    M1SKMM
     C                     Z-ADDUDAY      M1SKDD
     C                     UPDATMRAPL021
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     CSR         ESB580    ENDSR
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      * DATE                                               *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
     CSR         #SB800    BEGSR
      *
     C                     CALL 'DATR10'
     C                     PARM           PDATE   8
     C                     PARM           PRTN    1
      *
     CSR         ESB800    ENDSR
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      * CHECK  BLANK PATH-THRU                             *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
     CSR         #SB810    BEGSR
      *
     C                     MOVEL'0'       GET     1
     C                     MOVELD1BHN1    #KSHN1
     C                     MOVELD1BHN2    #KSHN2
     C                     MOVELD1BHN3    #KSHN3
     C                     MOVELD1SEKB    #KSEKB
     C           KEYM11    SETLLMRAPL011
     C           KEYM11    READEMRAPL011                 20
     C           *IN20     DOWEQ'0'
     C           M1SKJY    IFEQ 'D'
     C           M1SKHZ    ANDLE*DATE
     C                     ELSE
     C           M1KENO    IFNE D1KENO
     C                     MOVEL'1'       GET
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
     C           KEYM11    READEMRAPL011                 20
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     CSR         ESB810    ENDSR
**
ER-1 INPUT CUSTOMER PART NO.
ER-2 INPUT CUSTOMER NAME.
ER-3 INPUT MASS PRODUCTION DATE.
ER-4 DATE ERROR.
ER-5 INPUT Y OR N.
ER-6 INPUT COMPLETE PART NO.
ER-7 INPUT BLANK PART NO.
ER-8 CAN'T INPUT PAST DATE.
ER-9 MASS PRODUCTION DATE MUST BE AFTER TOOL ORDER DATE.
ER-10 INPUT QUANTITY.
ER-11 INPUT PART OR COMPONENT.(1,2)
ER-12 INPUT PRODUCTION LOCATION.(1,2,3,4)
ER-13 THIS BLANK PART NO ALREADY REGISTED.
